{"tid":1750461,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我父母投左建制可能因為我太年輕","createTime":"2019-11-24T11:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T12:28:39.000Z","uid":264820,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28a537f7c0122f2ba5fde3feb45e292b212ba2d0","tid":1750461,"uid":264820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"‪我發現我老豆老母真中毒太深。‬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n‪事源因為我啊婆身體唔好，所以我老豆老母個個禮拜日都會返大陸睇佢，咁琴晚都有打聽到佢哋今日都會返大陸，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">諗住佢哋應該唔去投票</span></span>，所以我都冇做啲咩阻佢哋投票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 點知佢哋今日晨咁早七點幾起身去投完票先至返大陸.....‬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都估唔到佢哋會咁盡公民責任....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對唔住各位，我令建制多左兩票</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120e389e4ce294f852a79373739d19b99ad1137d","tid":1750461,"uid":218855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"40d6f03893243ab2a38a6a3b1f306993e2ad3daa","tid":1750461,"uid":337761,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"屌埋你老豆